Classification of  Animals 	  All animals share basic traits. But animals also show a lot of diversity. They range from simple sponges to complex humans. 
Major  Animal  Phyla 	  Members of the animal kingdom are divided into more than 30 phyla. Table 10.1 lists the nine phyla with the greatest number of species. Each of the animal phyla listed in the table has at least 10,000 species. 
